*Aleks* je pronašao novi posao. (Alex found a new job.)

*Aleksu* je bilo teško da se prilagodi novim uslovima. (It was difficult for Alex to adjust to the new conditions.)

*Aleksa* su svi obožavali. (Everybody loved Alex.)

*Aleksom* je vladala sreća. (Alex had luck on his side.)

*Aleksi* je bila velika čast da bude pozvan na večeru. (It was an honor for Alex to be invited to dinner.)

*Aleksa* je bilo lako ubediti da ode na putovanje. (It was easy to persuade Alex to go on a trip.)